---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  metadata={{
    title: 'HTTP Server API — OWON Developers',
    description:
      'REST API + server-side HTTPS integration for OWON IoT devices — device management, telemetry, webhooks, and OTA updates.',
  }}
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <nav class="hidden lg:block w-56 shrink-0 sticky top-24 self-start space-y-1">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-3 tracking-wider">Developers</p>
          <a
            href="/developers"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Overview</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/mqtt"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >MQTT Quick Start</a
          >
          <a href="/developers/api" class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary"
            >HTTP Server API</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/zigbee"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >ZigBee Clusters</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/ha"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Home Assistant &amp; Z2M</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/sdks"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >SDKs &amp; Libraries</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/examples"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Code Examples</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/changelog"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Firmware Changelog</a
          >
        </nav>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-default dark:text-slate-100">HTTP Server API</h1>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">
            REST API + server-side HTTPS integration for OWON IoT devices — manage devices, query telemetry, trigger OTA
            updates, and receive webhook events.
          </p>

          <!-- NEW: Server Integration Overview -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Server Integration Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">
              The OWON cloud platform can push real-time device events to your server via HTTPS webhooks. This enables
              event-driven architectures without polling.
            </p>

            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Architecture</h3>
              <div class="rounded bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-4 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
                <p class="mb-1">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Device</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">→ MQTT →</span>
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">OWON Cloud</span>
                </p>
                <p class="mb-1">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">OWON Cloud</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">→ HTTPS Webhook →</span>
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Your Server</span>
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Your Server</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">→ HTTPS API →</span>
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">OWON Cloud</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Registering a Webhook Callback URL</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">
                Configure your callback endpoint via the REST API or the OWON Cloud Console:
              </p>
              <div
                class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-4 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
              >
                <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-500 mb-1"># Register webhook</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">POST /webhooks</p>
                <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-500 mb-1">{'{'}</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">"url": "https://your-server.com/owon-webhook",</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">
                  "events": ["device.online", "device.offline", "device.data"],
                </p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">"secret": "your-webhook-secret"</p>
                <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-500 mb-1">{'}'}</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Webhook Event Types</h3>
              <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-sm">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Event</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Trigger</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 text-muted">Frequency</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="text-default dark:text-slate-300">
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">device.online</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"
                        >Device connects to MQTT broker</td
                      ><td class="py-2">On connection</td></tr
                    >
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">device.offline</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"
                        >Device disconnects (clean or unclean)</td
                      ><td class="py-2">On disconnect</td></tr
                    >
                    <tr
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">device.data</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"
                        >Device publishes telemetry</td
                      ><td class="py-2">Per report interval</td></tr
                    >
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Webhook Payload Format</h3>
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                <pre>{`{
  "event": "device.data",
  "device_id": "dev_7a3b9c",
  "timestamp": "2026-07-10T08:30:00Z",
  "data": {
    "voltage": 220.5,
    "current": 12.3,
    "power": 2712.15,
    "energy_kwh": 1847.6
  }
}`}</pre>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Signature Verification</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">
                Every webhook request includes an <code class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-1 rounded"
                  >X-OWON-Signature</code
                > header. Verify using HMAC-SHA256 with your webhook secret:
              </p>
              <div
                class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-4 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
              >
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200"># Node.js example:</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">const crypto = require('crypto');</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">const sig = req.headers['x-owon-signature'];</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">const expected = crypto</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">.createHmac('sha256', secret)</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">.update(JSON.stringify(req.body))</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">.digest('hex');</p>
                <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">
                  if (sig !== expected) throw new Error('Invalid signature');
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- NEW: Debugging Application -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Debugging Application</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">
              The OWON API Debugger app lets you inspect MQTT traffic, test API endpoints, and simulate device data —
              all from your mobile device.
            </p>
            <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 mb-4">
              <div
                class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 flex items-center gap-4"
              >
                <span class="text-3xl">🍎</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 text-sm">OWON API Debugger — iOS</h3>
                  <p class="text-xs text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-2">
                    MQTT monitor, API request builder, device simulator
                  </p>
                  <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-primary hover:underline font-medium">
                    Download on App Store →
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 flex items-center gap-4"
              >
                <span class="text-3xl">🤖</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 text-sm">OWON API Debugger — Android</h3>
                  <p class="text-xs text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-2">
                    MQTT monitor, API request builder, device simulator
                  </p>
                  <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-primary hover:underline font-medium">
                    Download APK →
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-4">
              <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Debugger Screens</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-default dark:text-slate-300 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                <li><strong>MQTT Monitor</strong> — Subscribe to topics and view live telemetry in real time</li>
                <li><strong>API Request Builder</strong> — Construct and send REST API requests with your API key</li>
                <li><strong>Device Simulator</strong> — Generate mock telemetry data to test your integration</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EXISTING: Authentication -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Authentication</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
              All API requests require an API key in the <code class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-1 rounded"
                >Authorization</code
              > header. Keys are issued per project — contact our engineering team to obtain one.
            </p>
            <div
              class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-4 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
            >
              <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-500 mb-1"># Every request must include:</p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Authorization:</span>
                <span class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">Bearer YOUR_API_KEY</span>
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Content-Type:</span>
                <span class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">application/json</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EXISTING: Base URL -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Base URL</h2>
            <div
              class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-4 font-mono text-sm"
            >
              <p>
                <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">https://</span><span
                  class="text-default dark:text-slate-200">api.owon-iot.com/v1</span
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EXISTING: Device Endpoints -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Device Management</h2>

            <!-- GET /devices -->
            <div class="mb-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700"
              >
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">GET</span>
                <code class="text-sm font-mono text-default dark:text-slate-200">/devices</code>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">List all devices under your project.</p>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Query Parameters</h4>
                <table class="w-full text-sm mb-4">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Name</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Type</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 text-muted">Description</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="text-default dark:text-slate-300">
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">page</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">int</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Page number (default: 1)</td
                      ></tr
                    >
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">limit</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">int</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)</td
                      ></tr
                    >
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">type</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">string</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Filter: <code>smart-meter</code>, <code>thermostat</code>, <code>sensor</code></td
                      ></tr
                    >
                    <tr
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">status</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">string</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Filter: <code>online</code>, <code>offline</code>, <code>all</code></td
                      ></tr
                    >
                  </tbody>
                </table>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Response 200</h4>
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                  <pre>{`{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "dev_7a3b9c",
      "name": "Office Meter A1",
      "type": "smart-meter",
      "status": "online",
      "firmware": "2.1.4",
      "last_seen": "2026-07-10T08:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "total": 42,
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 20
}`}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GET /devices/:id -->
            <div class="mb-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700"
              >
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">GET</span>
                <code class="text-sm font-mono text-default dark:text-slate-200">/devices/:id</code>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">
                  Get device details including current telemetry snapshot.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Response 200</h4>
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                  <pre>{`{
  "id": "dev_7a3b9c",
  "name": "Office Meter A1",
  "type": "smart-meter",
  "status": "online",
  "firmware": "2.1.4",
  "telemetry": {
    "voltage": 220.5,
    "current": 12.3,
    "power": 2712.15,
    "energy_kwh": 1847.6,
    "temperature": 34.2
  },
  "last_seen": "2026-07-10T08:30:00Z"
}`}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- POST /devices/:id/ota -->
            <div class="mb-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700"
              >
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-orange-500 text-white">POST</span>
                <code class="text-sm font-mono text-default dark:text-slate-200">/devices/:id/ota</code>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">
                  Trigger an OTA firmware update for a specific device.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Request Body</h4>
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto mb-3">
                  <pre>{`{
  "firmware_version": "2.2.0",
  "firmware_url": "https://firmware.owon-iot.com/v2.2.0.bin"
}`}</pre>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Response 202</h4>
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                  <pre>{`{
  "ota_id": "ota_9f2e1a",
  "device_id": "dev_7a3b9c",
  "status": "pending",
  "target_version": "2.2.0"
}`}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GET /devices/:id/telemetry -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700"
              >
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">GET</span>
                <code class="text-sm font-mono text-default dark:text-slate-200">/devices/:id/telemetry</code>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">
                  Query historical telemetry data with time range.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Query Parameters</h4>
                <table class="w-full text-sm mb-4">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Name</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Type</th>
                      <th class="text-left py-2 text-muted">Description</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="text-default dark:text-slate-300">
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">from</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">ISO 8601</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Start time (required)</td
                      ></tr
                    >
                    <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">to</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">ISO 8601</td><td class="py-2"
                        >End time (default: now)</td
                      ></tr
                    >
                    <tr
                      ><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">interval</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">string</td><td class="py-2"
                        >Aggregation: <code>1m</code>, <code>15m</code>, <code>1h</code>, <code>1d</code></td
                      ></tr
                    >
                  </tbody>
                </table>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-2">Response 200</h4>
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                  <pre>{`{
  "device_id": "dev_7a3b9c",
  "interval": "1h",
  "data": [
    { "ts": "2026-07-10T08:00:00Z", "power": 2710, "energy_kwh": 1847.6 },
    { "ts": "2026-07-10T09:00:00Z", "power": 2685, "energy_kwh": 1850.3 }
  ]
}`}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EXISTING: Rate Limits -->
          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-default dark:text-slate-200">Rate Limits</h2>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Tier</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-muted">Requests / min</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 text-muted">Burst</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-default dark:text-slate-300">
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                    ><td class="py-2 pr-4">Standard</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">120</td><td class="py-2">20</td></tr
                  >
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800"
                    ><td class="py-2 pr-4">Enterprise</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">600</td><td class="py-2">50</td></tr
                  >
                  <tr
                    ><td class="py-2 pr-4">Custom</td><td class="py-2 pr-4" colspan="2"
                      >Contact us for dedicated rate limits</td
                    ></tr
                  >
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EXISTING: Contact CTA -->
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-default dark:text-slate-200 font-medium mb-2">
              Need API access or custom integration support?
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
              Our engineering team can provision API keys and provide dedicated onboarding.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/contact-sales"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors font-medium text-sm"
            >
              Contact Engineering Team →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
